    "en": {
      "title": "Detention of a Russian-flagged ship in Turkey",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Turkey has detained a Russian-flagged cargo ship after Kiev authorities said it was involved in the illegal transport of grain from Ukraine.",
        "\"We have full support. The ship is currently at the entrance to the port, and it is being detained by the Turkish customs authorities and is being investigated,\" said the Ukrainian ambassador to Turkey.",
        "The move comes two days after Ukrainian diplomats asked Turkish authorities to detain the Shibek Sholi, arguing that it was transporting stolen Ukrainian agricultural products."
      ],
